name: details in the fabric #1
description:
This is gonna be a collection of photos made in a fabric during a student vacation job - 8hrs of thinking about life, seeing faces of workers who spent about +5yrs of their entire life doing the same routine behind <5 similar machines - life gets routinized, predictable - feelings extracted, 8hrs shifts to meditations 
made with an Iphone12, 5.3MB, edited with Lightroom
